prising employee tracking, time-attendance, library automation and management, and student information systems; and customized solutions consisting of automated binning systems, intelligent converters, GSM based mast or I/O controllers, GSM logic controllers, boom barriers, loop detectors, single and multi-line LED panels, and kiosk applications, as well as other customizable converters, counters, etc. In addition, it offers building solutions, including building management systems, services and technologies, i-BMS systems, energy services, lighting control products, and maintenance services. Further, the company provides visual effects, digital intermediate, high-resolution film scanning and film recording, and editing and motion control services to high-definition production. It serves road and transportation, infra and building, health and medical, defense, security and surveillance, and other sectors. The company was formerly known as Bhartiya Global Software Limited and changed its name to Bharatiya Global Infomedia Limited in November 2003. Bharatiya Global Infomedia Limited was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Noida, India."}}